  <RI_Sect_CallSectOrbitalBombardment.label>呼叫宗门轨道轰炸</RI_Sect_CallSectOrbitalBombardment.label>
  <!-- EN: Contact a sect elder to obtain the usage rights for a Heavenly-grade magic weapon, and conduct orbital bombardment on a specific area. -->
